    },
    {
      "text": "Ninja Reflex is a video game developed by Sanzaru Games, and co-published by Nunchuck Games and Electronic Arts. It was released for Wii and Nintendo DS in 2008. It was also released for the Steam service on March 21, 2008.\nNinja Reflex is a party game, capitalizing on the popularity of games that take advantage of the unique Nintendo Wii Remote motions seen in other titles including WarioWare: Smooth Moves, Mario Party 8, and Wii Sports. The objective of Ninja Reflex is to test players' reflexes and reaction times and challenge friends in head-to-head competition.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "닌자 리플렉스(Ninja Reflex)는 일렉트로닉 아츠가 개발한 Wii, 닌텐도 DS, 엑스박스 360, PC게임용 게임 소프트웨어이다.",
      "lang": "ko",
      "source": "wikipedia_ko"
    },
    {
      "text": "Ninja Reflex est un jeu vidéo de type party game développé par Sanzaru Games et édité par Nunchuck Games, sorti en 2008 sur Windows, Wii et Nintendo DS.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    },
    {
      "text": "Ninja Reflex è un videogioco sviluppato da Sanzaru Games e pubblicato da Electronic Arts.\nNel gioco ci sono diversi test, per esempio: prove di riflessi e di reazione dei giocatori.\nInoltre si possono sfidare gli amici nel concorso Head-to-Head.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Ninja Reflex』は、Sanzaru Gamesが開発し、Nunchuck GamesとElectronic Artsが共同パブリッシングしたビデオゲームです。2008年にWiiおよびNintendo DS向けに発売され、同年3月21日にはSteamサービスでもリリースされました。\n\n『Ninja Reflex』はパーティーゲームであり、『WarioWare: Smooth Moves』や『マリオパーティ8』、『Wii Sports』など、他のタイトルで展開されたユニークなNintendo Wiiリモコンの動きを利用したゲームの人気に乗ることを目指しています。このゲームの目的は、プレイヤーの反射神経と反応時間を試すことで、友人たちと対戦を繰り広げることです。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
